'''Nasir Chinyoti''' (ناصر چنیوٹی) is a [[Pakistan]]i actor.<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.dailyjinnah.com/?p=19259|periodical=Daily Jinnah|title=اداکار ناصر چنیوٹی بھی پروڈیوسر بن گئے|date=2009-05-16|accessdate=2009-09-22}}</ref> He is a comedian, stage, and TV actor. He is from [[Chiniot]]. He started his acting at [[Multan]] Stage.<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.stage.pk/nasir.html|title=Nasir Chinyoti - Pakistani Stage Actor|accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref> He has starred in many stage dramas/telefilms in various languages, including [[Urdu]] and [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]]. He is most notable for comedy stage dramas based in [[Lahore]]. He is famous for using improvised dialogue during stage plays. Nasir Chinyoti has acted with a number of other comedy actors including [[Babu Baral]], [[Sohail Ahmad]], [[Iftikhar Thakur]], [[Anwar Ali (actor)|Anwar Ali]], [[Tariq Teddy]], and [[Sakhawat Naz]]. He currently appears in [[Khabardaar]] Comedy Show in various satires on [[Express News (Pakistan)]].He is rated one of the best comedians in Pakistan.
